data.description: Cape in a desirable neighborhood situated on an acre corner lot.  Tons of potential. This home has enough space for everyone.  Enter through the breezeway to the open concept kitchen dining. Updated appliances and large center island.  Fireplaced living room.  First floor primary bedroom, full bath and laundry.  Two bedrooms and a half bath on the second floor.  Two additional flex rooms one above the garage and the other off the breezeway currently being used as an in-law.  Finished family room and additional room in the basement.  Two wood stoves.  Plenty of yard space and deck for all outside activities.  New roof on the home before closing. Logs will be removed from yard.
